Package BeamCalc

Class Summary
BeamControl  
CoordinateSystem This class implements a Coordinate System, and contains the methods necessary for the translation of one vector from a CS to another
DXFImporter This class imports parses DXF files and converts the line objects into element objects understandable by the solver
Element The class Element is where the calculation of the reactions and the internal stresses of the element takes place.
ElementData  
Gradient Gradient Class, used to create gradients containing the whole colour spectrum
Material Class containing the material properties of the element
Node This class contains the definitions of every node in the structure, the integration algorithms and the equilibrium equations.
OpenFileAction This action creates and shows a modal open-file dialog.
PDisp_Data  
Section This class contains the geometric data of the section
Structure The class Structure contains is the main class in the library.
Toolbox This class creates a java JFrame containing a Processing application containing all the controls of the solver.
